author: mgrigorov
msg: WICKET-3578 Wicket should set the character encoding on requests
Set the character encoding in WebApplication#newWebRequest(). This way the user may "disable" it if needed by overriding this factory method.

author: dashorst
msg: Fixed a regression between Wicket 1.4 and 1.5, where markup ID generation/retrieval caused runtime exceptions in cases where the component was not added to the Page yet. Improved the semantics of Component#getMarkupId() and encased it in a couple unit tests.

author: allee8285
msg: OPENJPA-1984 - Skip non-root object validation when performing remove(root object). Let's validation provider to perform root object validation so that the contraint violation can report the correct root bean.
